OL,3,CThermal imaging camera bolsters JLA's
OL,4,C'life or death' rescue capabilities
OL,6,FITV News Channel reporter Philip Sime
OL,7,Fwent along to see how it works...
OL,9,FJersey Lifeboat Association (JLA) says
OL,10,Fit is "humbled" after receiving a new
OL,11,Fthermal imaging camera as a donation,
OL,12,Fmaking it easier for the organisation
OL,13,Fto conduct sea searches at night.
OL,15,FThe new camera, worth over #17,000,
OL,16,Fwas given to the JLA by Building
OL,17,FRenovations Ltd and will allow the
OL,18,Flifeboat crew to track multiple
OL,19,Fthermal and radar targets to help
OL,20,Fquickly identify people in the water
OL,21,For along the coast.
