OL,3,CThermal imaging camera bolsters JLA's
OL,4,C'life or death' rescue capabilities
OL,6,FThe JLA says introducing the
OL,7,Ftechnology should also make it easier
OL,8,Fto work with other emergency services
OL,9,Fwhen they are called out to rescues.
OL,11,FThe JLA's previous camera will now be
OL,12,Frepurposed aboard the charity's all-
OL,13,Fweather vessel 'Sir Max'.
