OL,3,CThermal imaging camera bolsters JLA's
OL,4,C'life or death' rescue capabilities
OL,6,FJLA lifeboat crewmember Max Boleat
OL,7,Fsaid: "Whilst our vessel has had a
OL,8,Fthermal imaging capability since its
OL,9,Farrival, this new camera marks a
OL,10,Fsignificant improvement over the
OL,11,Fprevious installation including a gyro
OL,12,Fstabilisation system and larger
OL,13,Fsensors allowing for clearer and more
OL,14,Fstable images during searches.
OL,16,F"The new camera was used less than 48
OL,17,Fhours after commissioning as our ILB
OL,18,Fwas diverted from a routine training
OL,19,Fexercise & tasked by Jersey Coastguard
OL,20,Fto conduct a search on the north coast
OL,21,Freturning to station just after 2am.
