OL,3,CThermal imaging camera bolsters JLA's
OL,4,C'life or death' rescue capabilities
OL,6,F"The camera allows our crews to
OL,7,Fquickly identify & automatically track
OL,8,Fthermal targets during open water &
OL,9,Fcoastal searches."
OL,11,FJLA coxswain Alain Baudains told ITV
OL,12,FNews: "With the new technology,
OL,13,Fthermal imagine, we're able to pick up
OL,14,Fheat signatures and pick up people
OL,15,Fquicker than with standard torches.
OL,17,F"In a life or death situation, every
OL,18,Fsecond counts, every minute counts."
